40:03.542 --> 40:05.792
I'M WITH YOU.
WAIT, WAIT. UH,
BEFORE EVERYBODY LEAVES,

40:05.834 --> 40:07.083
I, UM...

40:07.125 --> 40:09.458
I JUST WANT TO SAY,
I'M SORRY.

40:09.500 --> 40:11.458
I-I--YOU HAVE TO KNOW
THAT I DIDN'T MEAN

40:11.500 --> 40:13.458
