ON ANY OF YOU.

40:13.500 --> 40:15.583
AND I JUST--I HAD NO IDEA.

40:15.625 --> 40:18.583
SO JUST SO YOU KNOW, I-I SPOKE
TO THE MEDICAL BOARD TODAY

40:18.625 --> 40:21.500
AND, UH, ANSWERED
